text: Bucharest Non Stop () is a 2015 Romanian comedy-drama movie directed by Dan Chișu and starring Gheorghe Ifrim, Ion Besoiu, Adrian Titieni, Dorina Lazăr, Dorian Boguță, Olimpia Melinte. ==Other websites== * Category:2015 comedy- drama movies Category:Romanian comedy movies Category:Romanian drama movies
